        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The weeks — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The seven weeks which you are to number from the passover. This fifth stated and national sacrifice was also annual, namely, at the harvest festival, when the first-fruits of corn were to be offered up, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 23:16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". This festival was two-fold; first, the barley- harvest first-fruits, beginning at the passover; and then, at seven weeks’ end, the wheat-harvest festival, called the feast of weeks, which is here intended. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "When ye bring a new meat ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "or ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "bread-offering — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That is, two loaves made of the first wheat flour, as the first-fruits of the said wheat- harvest.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
